No. 338,

Mise.

Oquendo v. United States. Conrad J. Lynn for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States. Marvin M. Karpatkin for Youth Against War & Fascism, as amicus curiae, in support of the petition.

C. A. 2d Cir. Motion of Youth Against War & Fascism for leave to file a brief, as amicus curiae, granted. Certio-rari denied.
